          <p class="text-sm">
            Sneaker Lab is the only shoe care brand that puts nature first. Our products are made from
            environmentally friendly ingredients and are 100% biodegradable; making us the only shoe care
            brand that puts nature first.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="border-t border-silver text-xs md:text-sm">
          <button class="flex accordion-trigger justify-between items-center w-full uppercase py-3 text-left"
                  aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-item-3" id="accordion-title-3">
            Delivery &amp; Returns
